005C89E2.VoiceDir5.F53E7: Strike a balance between caring and professional. You are responsible for training Aneta.

2B479923.Line7.F52ED: It still hurts when they speak...they all talk over each other...I'm sorry...

34457CE6.VoiceDir9.F53E7: Said like a well-known phrase you've told your student many times. Witches don't apologize.

5D6A2C9D.Line1.F52ED: (sigh) Yes... yes. Thank you. I'll be all right. Gulyas' ritual is just... draining...

66681060.VoiceDir3.F53E7: Disappointed mom voice. The player meant well but they could have hurt your young ward with their carelessness.

727514C2.Line11.F53E7: Hmm. Something still enflames your blood. There is only one thing left to try.

915323B5.Line5.F53E7: Have the voices quieted, Aneta? Can you understand them yet?

9A50FF50.VoiceDir7.F52ED: Scared of letting your teacher who you look up to down. Slightly ashamed of your lack of progress.

C2AB408F.VoiceDir11.F53E7: Curious. Thinking it through as you speak. A bit disappointed on the last sentence, you were hoping to avoid having to bring out the big guns.

C53C16B9.Line9.F53E7: We don't apologize for things outside our control.

F75EAA33.Line3.F53E7: Only when meddled with by well-meaning but ignorant visitors.
